NOTE ON MODELS & DATASETS (third-party, separate licenses — verified on the HF Hub):
- Trainable backbones: google-t5/t5-small (Apache-2.0); google/byt5-small (Apache-2.0);
  facebook/m2m100_418M (MIT). Pose/CSLR references: manohonsy/how2sign-pose-cslr (MIT);
  sign/sockeye-signwriting-to-text (MIT). Video front-end: microsoft/xclip-base-patch32 (MIT).
  Pose front-end: MediaPipe Holistic (Apache-2.0, Google).
- AVOID (non-commercial): MCG-NJU/videomae-base (CC-BY-NC); sign/mediapipe-vq (CC-BY-NC-SA).
- Datasets: Sigurdur/icelandic-sign-language (Apache-2.0, permissive smoke test);
  om192006/sign_language_keypoints (MIT). FLAGGED (non-commercial / gated / unspecified):
  Exploration-Lab/iSign (CC-BY-NC-SA, gated); aipieces/How2Sign + PSewmuthu/How2Sign_Holistic
  (How2Sign is CC-BY-NC upstream); Voxel51/WLASL (license:other); Kibalama/poseformer-sign-language.
  RWTH-PHOENIX-2014T / CSL-Daily / YouTube-ASL are NOT redistributable HF repos (academic licenses).
Every continuous sign-language corpus found is non-commercial / gated / unspecified — verify and
comply with each upstream license before any use. This MIT license covers ONLY the code in this
repository, not the third-party models/datasets. The synthetic pose generator is the primary data.
